Yak Changelog
=============

Logging changes between PyPI Yak releases.

Version 0.1.5
-------------

- More extensive configuration options for main page and ATOM post count

Version 0.1.4
-------------

- Changed Yak blog initialization command (yak --build-base -> yak init)
- Better image handling
- Fixed encoding issues
- Yak now prints the time it took to read the posts from storage
- Added CSS3 column-count for archive listing

Version 0.1.3
-------------

- Fixed README file issue
- Fixed ATOM updated datetime bug
- Fixed minor bugs

Version 0.1.2
-------------

- Modified some CSS line-heights

Version 0.1.1
-------------

- Yak now uses tempfile.mkdtemp() to create temporary baking directory

Version 0.1
-----------

- Initial public release
